@{
    ViewData["Title"] = "Privacy Policy";
}
<h1 class="text-center">@ViewData["Title"]</h1>

<div class="container mt-4" style="background-color: white; padding: 20px; border-radius: 10px; box-shadow: 0 4px 6px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);">
    
    <p>
        Welcome to the <strong>Smith Swimming School</strong> Privacy Policy. At our swimming school, we value and respect your privacy. This document explains how we collect, use, and protect your personal information.
    </p>

    <h2>1. Information We Collect</h2>
    <p>We may collect the following information about our students, coaches, and users:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Full name</li>
        <li>Date of birth</li>
        <li>Contact information (such as email address and phone number)</li>
        <li>Enrollment history in courses and programs</li>
        <li>Performance and progress data in swimming classes</li>
        <li>Health or special needs information (if provided voluntarily)</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
    <p>The information we collect is used solely for the following purposes:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Register students in our courses and programs.</li>
        <li>Communicate important information about schedules, classes, and events.</li>
        <li>Personalize the teaching experience according to the student's needs.</li>
        <li>Maintain a record of progress in classes.</li>
        <li>Comply with legal and regulatory requirements.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>3. Protecting Your Information</h2>
    <p>
        We implement physical, electronic, and administrative security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, alteration, or destruction.
    </p>

    <h2>4. Sharing Your Information</h2>
    <p>
        We do not share your personal information with third parties without your consent, except in the following cases:
    </p>
    <ul>
        <li>With government or legal authorities when required by law.</li>
        <li>With external service providers who assist us in operating the school (such as payment platforms).</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>5. User Rights</h2>
    <p>You have the right to:</p>
    <ul>
        <li>Access your personal information stored by us.</li>
        <li>Request the correction or deletion of your personal information.</li>
        <li>Withdraw your consent for the use of your personal information at any time.</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>6. Contact</h2>
    <p>
        If you have any questions or concerns about our privacy policy, please feel free to contact us:
    </p>
    <p>
        <strong>Smith Swimming School</strong><br />
        Email: <a href="">info@smithswimming.com</a><br />
        Phone: +1 (123) 456-7890<br />
        Address: 123 Swimming Lane, Aqua City, AC 12345
    </p>

    <h2>7. Policy Updates</h2>
    <p>
        We reserve the right to update this privacy policy at any time. We will notify you of significant changes through our website or via email.
    </p>
</div>
